# Repo-root .vercelignore — used by the STATIC FRONTEND Vercel project (Root
# Directory = repo root). Exclude the API source tree so Vercel doesn't try to
# build api/ as serverless functions for the frontend deploy. The API has its
# own Vercel project (Root Directory = api/) which is unaffected by this file.
# api  ← TEMP-DISABLED to diagnose the API git build (#3)
